272
00:21:29,501 --> 00:21:30,711
Baik, Baginda.

273
00:21:52,983 --> 00:21:53,859
Tapi...

274
00:22:00,032 --> 00:22:01,867
<font color="#ffff00">JEONG TAE-EUL.</font>

275
00:22:06,288 --> 00:22:07,581
<i>Ini ruang kendali.</i>

276
00:22:08,040 --> 00:22:11,668
